&lt;h1 id="yes-the-bubble-is-back"&gt;Yes, the bubble is back&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dec 16 2005&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yes, the bubble is back&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just take a look at the domain name sales on &lt;a href="http://dnjournal.com/"&gt;DNJournal&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href="http://fish.com/"&gt;Fish.com&lt;/a&gt; goes for over $1 Million! [Alarm clock](http://alarmclock.com/), otherwise a great resource, is still living in the pre-bubble days, when [domain sales of $100k were news](&lt;a href="http://alarmclock.com/neo/2005/12/domain_sales_100k.html%29"&gt;http://alarmclock.com/neo/2005/12/domain_sales_100k.html)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>What the Bubble Got Right</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/bubble/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/bubble/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/bubble/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
